<HEADLINE>
<P>
'THE VEIL' TO BENEFIT BET TZEDEK LEGAL CLIENTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A benefit production of "The Veil," Henry Slesar's holiday mystery, featuring 
James Dumont, Lisa Thames, Pamel Shafer and Nancy Linehan Charles, is running 
today and Sunday at the Tiffany Theatre in West Hollywood. 
</P>
<P>
 All proceeds will benefit Bet Tzedek Legal Services, a nonprofit organization 
providing free legal services to indigent clients. 
</P>
<P>
 Tickets are $50. 
</P>
<P>
 Reservations: (310) 289-2999. 
</P>
