BORISKIN RECITAL POSTPONED TILL MARCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Michael Boriskin's recital of 20th-Century piano music that was scheduled for 
Monday at the Los Angeles County Museum of Art has been postponed until March 
20 because the pianist is suffering from flu. Tickets will be honored at that 
time. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: (213) 857-6115. 
</P>
