three-pointers over a three-minute stretch in the second half for the Aggies at 
Las Cruces, N.M. 
</P>
<P>
 Wyatt finished with 18 points and and Rodney Walker had 15 for New Mexico 
State (6-2). New Mexico is 3-3. 
