<HEADLINE>
<P>
METROPOLITAN DIGEST / LOS ANGELES COUNTY NEWS IN BRIEF: VAN NUYS; MAN, 69, 
CONVICTED IN MOLESTATION OF 3 GIRLS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A 69-year-old Reseda man will be sentenced next month for sexually molesting 
several teen-age girls who visited his home on a series of occasions in 1993 
and early this year, Deputy Dist. Atty.George Schell said Friday.  
</P>
<P>
 William Bud Brown was convicted in Van Nuys earlier this week of one count of 
sexual battery and two counts each of child molestation and child abuse. 
</P>
<P>
 The charges grew out of incidents involving three teen-age girls, who 
testified that they had been molested by Brown, Schell said. 
</P>
