<DOCID> 106788 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 10, 1994, Saturday, Valley Edition Correction Appended 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
