79-yard touchdown pass play from Nathan Judd to Ty Gifford early in the second 
quarter. 
</P>
<P>
 Chris Fick, who scored Boron's first touchdown on two-yard run, finished with 
96 yards in 22 carries. 
</P>
<P>
 Morro Bay, playing in its first championship, finished 10-2. ROB LEHOCKY 
