<DOCNO> LA121094-0263 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 106894 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 10, 1994, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
