payments. They must be postmarked by Dec. 12 or delivered by 6 p.m. to the 
county treasurer-tax collector's office at 800 S. Victoria Ave. in Ventura. 
Taxpayers also can use a drop box near the main entrance of the county 
Administration Building. The drop box hours are 8 a.m. to 5 p.m. today and 
Sunday, and from 6 p.m. through midnight on Monday. 
</P>
